{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 181.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at that time, I went to work outside the ghetto with my husband and another group of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we'd sleep-- we used to sleep there, outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "For a whole week, we were working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then for the weekend, for one day, they-- soldiers used to take us to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we'd go back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, for the weekend, we'd go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And like this, we worked in the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the Wehrmacht, was working a lot of different things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My first jobs were cleaning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Like we used to-- I started in 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I used to clean houses, clean barracks, wash laundry, carry water up to the second or third floor, do anything that-- like household work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was-- that was my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then I, I went on the Kommando, and we used to do streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So we used to carry stones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they used to pave streets, make-- fix sidewalks, and all the other things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I used to work alongside with men for, for months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then afterwards, when winter came along, and I started to work again-- so they used to send us out in the biggest snow and frost to wash the barracks outside.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was their big thing so we could have to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we could freeze.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so we did this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was in 1942, towards the end of 1942, when they made the ghetto smaller and they started to bring in more people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then it was Weihnacht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Weihnacht means New Year's.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they came into the ghetto and just out of the blue sky, started to shoot people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And afterwards, they went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
